  - Tightened CTA to `Fix letter names` instead of vague win/unlock wording.

- `scripts/qa_module2_production_mobile.mjs`
  - Browser guard now supports no-typing speak+repair missions across M1/M2.
  - Fixed repair-choice matching per mission instead of hardcoding one answer.
  - Handles 2-option repair steps like spelling.

- `scripts/qa_intro_start_path.mjs`
  - Made browser QA wait for actual route content before asserting, avoiding false failures on slow Next route hydration.

- `scripts/qa_mission_pilot.py`
  - Added guard for M1 please-thanks staying voice-first/no-typing.
  - Updated M1 mission checks to allow `SpeakRepairStep`, not only `SpeakWriteStep`.

